name: Rin Finance Coin
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
Rin Finance Coin is the native currency of the Rin Finance  ecosystem
of blockchain events.

Through annual awards and recognition events, we aim to play a pivotal
role in the blockchain ecosystem by

Fostering healthy competition
Celebrating achievements
Highlighting innovations

Built on the  Binance Smart Chain, the coin gives holders voting rights
to events organized on our platform. There is currently no minimum
requirement of tokens user can hold to vote.
